'''Secrets of Gloomrot''' (version 0.6.0.57108, released May 17, 2023) was the first major Early Access update, officially titled ''Update #1: Secrets of Gloomrot''. It added the [[Gloomrot]] biome, a full spell rework with the [[Jewels|Jewel]] system, two new weapon types ([[Greatsword]] and [[Pistols]]), map updates, multi-floor castle territories, shapeshifting updates and trade hub updates.

==Hotfixes==
Eleven hotfixes shipped between May 18 and October 25, 2023 (0.6.1 through 0.6.10) — see the [[Patch Notes]] index for the individual Steam announcements.

